Areva, Toshiba to Get $2.2 Billion EDF Generator Order, La Tribune Reports

-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 
2011-09-28T04:48:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/areva-toshiba-to-get-2-2-billion-edf-generator-order-la-tribune-reports.html
Electricite de France SA is set to
award a 1.6 billion-euro contract for 11 steam generators to
Areva SA and Toshiba-Westinghouse, La Tribune reported, without
saying where it got the information.  EDF’s board will today approve the order for eight Areva
generators and three from Toshiba-Westinghouse, according to the
French daily newspaper. Areva’s share of the contract is worth
1.1 billion euros, La Tribune said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Rhinds at 
 srhinds@bloomberg.net  